title: Hoover WindTunnel Air Brush Roll Not Spinning?
description: Hi Terry. The brushes on the Air should spin without any issue. We think either the brush roll may have been accidentally turned off, or it may be jammed. We put together a quick video to help you get it working again. Let us know if you need more help! -
